<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
Dear <%= @new_user.name %>,
<p>
  A login to the <%= APPLICATION_NAME %> website has been set up for you by <%= mail_to @added_by.email, @added_by.name %>.
  Here is your new login information:
</p>

<div><strong>Web address:</strong> <%= @main_app_url %></div>
<div><strong>Username:</strong> <%= @new_user.email %></div>

<p>
  You can log in and set up your password using this link:
  <%= link_to @password_reset_url, @password_reset_url %>
</p>
<p>
  This link will be valid for the next <%= pluralize(@hours_to_log_in,"hour") %>.
</p>
<p>
  If you don't log in and set up your password in the next <%= pluralize(@hours_to_log_in,"hour") %>, no worries.
  You can request an updated link anytime by going to <%= link_to 'Reset Password', password_forgot_url %>
</p>

<p>
  <%=@contact_if_questions_msg %>
</p>

</body>
</html>